FBIS4-29554 "dreas118_c_94012" FBIS-EAS-94-118 Daily Report 17 Jun 1994 North Korea WPK Secretary Meets Delegation From Japan's LDP WPK Secretary Meets Delegation From Japan's LDP SK1706114594 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1110 GMT 17 Jun 94 SK1706114594 Pyongyang KCNA English BFN [Text] Pyongyang, June 17 (KCNA) -- Secretary of the C.C. [Central Committee], the Workers' Party of Korea [WPK] Hwang Chang-yop today met and conversed in a friendly atmosphere with a delegation of the Japan Liberal Democratic Party [LDP] headed by Taku Yamasaki, deputy secretary general of the party and member of the house of representatives, at the Mansudae Assembly Hall. Present there was vice department director of the WPK Central Committee Kim Yang-kon.
